newsitem.title: UK: NWE jet fuel firm, refinery material scarce.
newsitem.headline: NWE jet fuel firm, refinery material scarce.

text.p: NWE jet fuel was firmer on Thursday with buyers looking outside the region for large cargoes of refinery material, traders said.
"There's good supplies in storage, but not out of refineries," a trader said.
Buyers were seen talking to producers in the Mideast and the Carribean for fob barrels.
A few smaller parcels were on offer in NWE at around Oct IPE +37, while barge talk was also firm at around Oct +$31.
Benchmark IPE gas oil Oct futures gained $3 to close at $234.50 a tonne. --London Newsroom +44 171 542 5387
